Can you tell me a sweet bedtime story?
Once upon a time, there was a cute little white
rabbit who lived in a beautiful meadow. Every
night, he would wear a red Santa hat, sit on the
grass, look at the stars, and imagine tomorrow's
Christmas. It believes that Christmas gifts will
fall from the sky and surprise it. One day, it
really received a gift, which was a red Christmas
hat. It was very happy. From then on, it wore this
hat every day and enjoyed the joy of Christmas.
